## Query Optimization Rules

- Prefer select over include in Prisma queries.
- Never use include: true.
- List views must limit related data (e.g. take: 1 photo).
- Use Promise.all for parallel queries.
- Never introduce N+1 patterns.
- Paginated queries must use database-level pagination.
